&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience working with Axiom on engagements as an ALP.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active bar membership in good standing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and analytical skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive in dynamic, fast-paced environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for innovation in legal practice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Axiom?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexibility:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Choose assignments that fit your lifestyle and career goals.&lt;/li&gt;
