&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking &lt;strong&gt;Banking &amp;amp; Finance Lawyers&lt;/strong&gt; to work with a variety of Axiom clients across financial services, investment, real estate, infrastructure, and other industry sectors, supporting a broad range of lending, real estate finance, asset finance, secured finance, and cross-border financing matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide practical, commercially focused legal advice on banking and finance matters, including general lending, real estate finance, asset finance, secured lending, acquisition finance, refinancing, and cross-border financing transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise lenders, borrowers, investors, financial institutions, and corporate stakeholders on commercial real estate finance, property development finance, investment finance, asset-backed lending, receivables finance, and structured lending arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft, review, and negotiate finance documentation, including loan facility agreements, LMA-based documentation, security documents, intercreditor agreements, guarantees, ancillary finance documents, and transaction-related commercial agreements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with internal legal, finance, treasury, commercial, risk, investment, property, and external counsel teams to support domestic and international transactions, manage legal risk, and deliver pragmatic advice in fast-paced deal environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualified lawyer eligible to practise in the UK, or equivalent overseas qualification with strong UK banking and finance experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience advising on banking and finance transactions, including general lending, real estate finance, property finance, asset finance, secured lending, refinancing, or cross-border finance matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong drafting, review, and negotiation experience across facility agreements, security packages, intercreditor agreements, guarantees, ancillary finance documents, LMA-based documentation, or other lending documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent commercial awareness, drafting ability, stakeholder management, communication, and analytical skills, with the ability to deliver practical, business-focused advice to lenders, borrowers, investors, and corporate stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Compensation, Benefits &amp;amp; Location:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
